narratives.question_text: What was valuable about this class, either in format or content?
comments: Deep knowledge in the workings of studio recording hardware and its software management
Learned new approaches to many specific purposes. knew the recording software Pro Tools better.

narratives.question_text: Are there adjustments, additions or deletions that might be beneficial?
comments: It's probably not a good idea to count our completeness of assignment on many external conditions like music band, actors etc. I don't think the goal of taking this class is only to use the studio and equipment we have. It's more important to me to get the general idea and apply what we learned to what we will be doing in the future.

narratives.question_text: Were there any particular challenges that were difficult to overcome?
comments: Sometimes collaborating with other schools (not being in contact with at a frequent basis) turned out to be difficult.

narratives.question_text: Do you have any comments about the teaching/learning environment?
comments: I feel very good about the teaching/learning environment. It is relaxing and appealing.
